pageProduct.name: Andalou Age Defying BioActive Berry Fruit Enzyme Mask 50g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Fruit Stem Cells from the Apple & Grape, Resveratrol CoQ10, and antioxidant rich BioActive Berry complex help support dermal vitality. Fruit Juice Enzymes from Cranberry, Apple and Lemon gently dissolve and exfoliate dull, dry surface cells to reveal skin's natural glow and a youthful, rejuvenated complexion.

Warnings

For external use only. Avoid direct contact with eyes.

Common Uses

Facial Mask For Dry, Very Dry Skin Types

Ingredients

Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice*, Purified Water (Aqua), Vaccinium Macrocarpon (Cranberry) Fruit Juice*, Vegetable Glycerin, Hydroxypropyl Starch Phosphate, Fruit Stem Cells (Malus Domestica, Solar Vitis) and BioActive Berry Complex*, Resveratrol, Ubiquinone (CoQ10), Papain, Lecithin, Tocopherol, Saccharum Officinarum (Sugar Cane) Extract, Algae Extract, Leptospermum Scoparium (Manuka) Leaf Oil, Agave Tequilana Leaf Extract, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil*, Limnanthes Alba (Meadowfoam) Seed Oil, Pyrus Malus (Apple) Fruit Extract, Xanthan Gum, Citrus Medica Limonum (Lemon) Fruit Extract, Camellia Sinensis (White Tea) Leaf Extract*†, Hibiscus Sabdariffa Flower Extract*†, Aspalathus Linearis (Rooibos) Extract*†, Phenethyl Alcohol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Raspberry Isolates, Vanilla Isolates, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Peel Oil* *Certified Organic Ingredients †Fair Trade Ingredients

Directions

Apply evenly to clean, dry or damp skin. Leave for 10-20 minutes. Rinse with cool water.
